summary: This document certifies ownership of Units in ITHAX Acquisition Corp III, each consisting of one Class A ordinary share and half of a redeemable warrant, which allows the holder to purchase one share at $11.50. The Units cannot be separated until 2026, and the Warrants expire five years after the initial Business Combination. Holders are entitled to funds from a trust account if shares are redeemed or if the company liquidates without completing a Business Combination.
